                    <head>No. 121.<lb/><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Beach</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Bayard.</persName></hi></head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Guayaquil</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-08-11"><hi rend="italic">August</hi> 11, 1885</date>.
                            (Received August 11.)</dateline></opener>
                    <p rend="flushleft">Secretary <hi rend="smallcaps">Bayard</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington:</hi></p>
                    <p>Information positive that Santos liberated.</p>
                    <closer><signed>BEACH.</signed></closer>
